WEBVTT

00:00:06.793 --> 00:00:08.921
Insoniyat tarixi davomida,

00:00:08.921 --> 00:00:12.384
uch kichik so'z 
shoirlarni "bo'sh sahifa"ga,

00:00:12.384 --> 00:00:14.762
faylasuflarni esa keng maydon sari,

00:00:14.762 --> 00:00:17.102
izlanuvchilarni esa bo'shliqqa etaklaydi:

00:00:17.102 --> 00:00:19.099
"Men o'zi kimman?"

00:00:19.099 --> 00:00:22.723
Apollon Ibodatxonasiga yozilgan 
qadimgi yunon aforizmdan boshlab,

00:00:22.723 --> 00:00:24.459
"O'zingni angla,"

00:00:24.459 --> 00:00:27.192
"Who" guruhining "Sen kimsan?" qo'shig'i-

00:00:27.192 --> 00:00:30.312
gacha faylasuflar, psixologlar, 
mutafakkirlar,